INSERT INTO `preferences` VALUES (1,1,5,'This game is awesome!'),(2,1,4,'Fun game. I keep getting killed though :('),(1,4,2,'rip s2'),(1,3,4,'Still waiting for that GTA VI...'),(1,2,5,'You can build a ton of things.'),(17,3,5,'5/5 stars. I love committing violent crimes with friends (in video games, of course). I am a hacker and loop/auto-kill newbies in online mode. If you\'re a hacker like me, this is the game for you.'),(17,4,1,'Used to be a fun and enjoyable game, until the admins banned me for hacking. Now, I will have no choice but to take my hacking powers elsewhere. I would rate 0/5 if I could.'),(9,4,5,'My son Jotaro loves this game!'),(11,3,4,'I, Jotaro Kujo, am a juvenile delinquent and find this game to be quite enjoyable. '),(11,4,1,'Shut up mom, I hate this stupid game. They hardware banned me for hacking, but I told them that the only reason I was hacking was to fight other hackers, namely DIO. They do not care about justice.'),(10,1,4,'A fun game my husband and I enjoy playing together. Sometimes relaxing but sometimes it can be irritating. Overall a good game though.'),(10,2,5,'My favorite game. Very peaceful and relaxing. You can build anything, and creative mode is fun when you\'re looking to chill. '),(19,2,5,'Super fun game, I usually turn on God mode so I don\'t get bothered by newbies and mobs. I have creative mode irl so this is an enjoyable game for me. 5/5.'),(19,1,3,'It\'s pretty much a worse version of Minecraft. It\'s still fun, but nowhere near as enjoyable in my opinion. It is cheaper, however. '),(19,3,5,'I, Giorno Giovanna, have a dream... TO BECOME THE WORLD\'S GREATEST GANG-STAR IN GTAV AND IRL!'),(202,108,5,'THE FIGHTING IS GREAT'),(11,101,5,'I love punching and beating other people up in video games. 5/5.'),(11,108,5,'METAKNIGHT FOR LIFE!!!'),(20,101,4,'Still waiting on a hamon user playable character, but myself will do for now. '),(99,2,5,'I love dirt, and I love this digging/mining simulator. I play solely on creative mode and farm dirt blocks for hours on end. Sometimes I find and explore caves. Very fun game.'),(99,105,2,'I love mining and digging, but this game is too annoying. It would be more fun if I stopped getting killed all of the time. I just want to spelunk in peace. :('),(99,1,4,'Not as good as Minecraft, but still a very fun game nonetheless. The mobs can be super annoying though, especially on Master Mode.'),(91,107,2,'A fun premise, level designing is cool. However, the level of violence offends me, especially against the Koopas. Turtle gang for life, we deserve better!!'),(91,106,1,'A second game involving violence against Koopas?? Are you serious?? Nintendo must be stopped for their crimes against the turtle race!!'),(26,102,5,'Everyone knows that the best defense is a good offense. This is why Sword>Shield. '),(26,103,3,'The exclusive gym leaders and pokemon are cool, but Zacian>Zamazenta every day. Sword beats shield.'),(26,3,4,'My dad is a mob boss and tried to kill me. I joined a rival gang and we ended up killing him instead though, so it\'s a win. Overall, a really fun game.'),(26,104,4,'This game is really easy with powers like mine. Bullets cannot touch me, they are far too soft and weak. Try harder next game, COD kids.'),(28,101,5,'I am the best there is. I have over a billion mastery points in Min Min alone. Get on my level, skids.'),(28,108,5,'Metaknight too OP. That\'s why I play him.'),(28,145,5,'Wattson best character'),(99,124,5,'There\'s so much to explore and do in Skyrim, literally hundreds of hours. Possibly the greatest game of our generation. I am an avid caver and enjoy exploring the many caves Skyrim has to offer.'),(103,145,5,'I approve of this game. '),(103,122,5,'Every sane person knows that Eevee is the superior choice to that lame yellow rat, Pikachu. I named mine Metallica (naturally), and she is my Queen.'),(103,121,1,'METALLICA FOR LIFE!!! (That\'s what I named my Eevee, who is WAY cuter/better than the ugly yellow rat, Pikachu.'),(203,2,3,'very good');
